{"tid":1578274,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"何妖，記得清得乾淨啲啊","createTime":"2019-09-18T05:36:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T06:31:00.000Z","uid":21482,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3fed9529ca0570c93c69ace6e2309a53da8fbbf2","tid":1578274,"uid":21482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T05:36:58.000Z","msg":"既然人地咁大方請哂人幫我地清乾淨方便貼新文宣，我地不如920就貼定大字叫佢地清乾淨啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n與其硬碰，不如等佢地覺得自己on9<br />\n何妖谷左咁耐筆維穩費一野射哂出去，班廢老死捽爛捽大半日先清得完<br />\n幅牆第二日就整翻，上次坑口即晚起完，我地根本無需要花心思應付<br />\n<br />\n到班廢老過兩日行過，就會覺得自己比人撚<br />\n<br />\n其實最重要既係手足，一幅牆幾疊A4一晚搞得掂既事，真係無需要用手足去換，宜家班黑狗齋咬後生，為幅牆，真係唔值"},{"pid":"427c3fd917ef099d8544151f390a39d41ace55f7","tid":1578274,"uid":232229,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T05:44:46.000Z","msg":"都唔明清黎做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第2日就復活"},{"pid":"2d13d4b4b7d02fad5606100812dddec7d075ecdd","tid":1578274,"uid":270956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T05:45:47.000Z","msg":"Yup <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bac014016734d004be1f02735303f23412baf283","tid":1578274,"uid":36113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T05:48:19.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"e6126fe3b84f81516947fa39f6e54a4489da50c4","tid":1578274,"uid":68598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"427c3fd917ef099d8544151f390a39d41ace55f7","tid":1578274,"uid":232229,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T05:44:46.000Z","msg":"都唔明清黎做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第2日就復活"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T05:49:35.000Z","msg":"佢唔清邊有位貼新野<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e87a62bf0b45d33bfbc170a5ab8e1fdbb4e7c0b8","tid":1578274,"uid":21482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"427c3fd917ef099d8544151f390a39d41a